summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 15W, page 61, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Ravenna Springs Park Supplement, Portion of lots 3, 4, 5, lying east of Ravenna Place, Block 9, located on the northwest corner of Ravenna Place and Blakely St. as General Commercial (CG) Zone.
